description:
NFT in 5 years. 
Modern technology is advancing at a tremendous speed these days. It's scary to imagine how far we can go in 5 years. I think that in 5 years there will be a huge number of marketplaces, and the works of nft artists will be shown in galleries, and by the way they are already being shown. Traditional art will be sidelined, more and more digital artists will be involved. There will be a technological revolution in people's minds and in the life of contemporary and modern art.
